age.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.035904,0.049437,0.061084,0.073723,0.086435,0.097613,0.10669,0.10845,0.11265,0.11681,0.092387,0.058814],"unified_progress":[0.037093,0.058825,0.076618,0.086796,0.093609,0.10422,0.10081,0.10015,0.095597,0.09222,0.081504,0.072563]},{"section":7,"text":"It's known for causing muscle weakness and a waddling gait because the muscles get weaker and bigger, which makes sense here since they mentioned hypertrophy of the calf muscles.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.039901,0.04832,0.057515,0.068789,0.080166,0.09013,0.099271,0.10273,0.10935,0.11958,0.10859,0.075652],"unified_progress":[0.041856,0.059257,0.073582,0.083425,0.090588,0.099854,0.098711,0.10012,0.098479,0.094312,0.085704,0.074116]},{"section":8,"text":"Oh, and then there's the elevated CPK level.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.019987,0.052882,0.079078,0.099676,0.10937,0.11202,0.10928,0.10426,0.099783,0.095573,0.075645,0.042441],"unified_progress":[0.032313,0.066064,0.081596,0.094259,0.099566,0.09837,0.09887,0.096719,0.097977,0.093254,0.078063,0.062948]},{"section":9,"text":"Wow, it's really high at 10,000 IU!","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.028179,0.061921,0.087642,0.11145,0.12167,0.12005,0.11182,0.09582,0.083485,0.073953,0.061191,0.042827],"unified_progress":[0.036786,0.066725,0.085223,0.10101,0.1037,0.10107,0.10018,0.094246,0.095193,0.080377,0.070926,0.064565]},{"section":10,"text":"That's way above normal.","dimension":0,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.033153,0.088045,0.10404,0.11567,0.11628,0.11318,0.10384,0.088129,0.080624,0.066985,0.054061,0.035988],"unified_progress":[0.03877,0.076556,0.094897,0.10252,0.10896,0.10182,0.10594,0.091768,0.086103,0.074735,0.066019,0.051906]},{"section":11,"text":"High CPK levels usually mean muscle damage or breakdown, which fits with the muscle weakness and hypertrophy we're seeing here.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.033592,0.058836,0.074884,0.088501,0.095883,0.098242,0.09796,0.092646,0.09139,0.094167,0.095839,0.07806],"unified_progress":[0.039153,0.061626,0.078688,0.087822,0.094893,0.097949,0.10134,0.095705,0.093752,0.088481,0.084324,0.076263]},{"section":12,"text":"In Duchenne Muscular Dystrophy, the muscle cells break down and release CPK into the blood, so that would explain the high levels.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.026959,0.04329,0.060078,0.076573,0.088464,0.09625,0.10136,0.099902,0.10195,0.1095,0.10696,0.088704],"unified_progress":[0.032922,0.052475,0.070058,0.08158,0.089265,0.098368,0.09742,0.098822,0.099761,0.095386,0.092753,0.091191]},{"section":13,"text":"So, putting all these clues together - the age, the symptoms, the gait, the muscle hypertrophy, and the sky-high CPK levels - everything points towards Duchenne Muscular Dystrophy.","dimension":8,"group":9,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.016749,0.030339,0.040805,0.05054,0.060256,0.069582,0.080801,0.089365,0.10348,0.12858,0.16713,0.16238],"unified_progress":[0.025836,0.041526,0.053585,0.064267,0.074268,0.087487,0.09036,0.098548,0.10654,0.11137,0.12192,0.12429]},{"section":14,"text":"Yeah, I'm pretty confident that's what's going on here.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.089149,0.072057,0.06809,0.062589,0.06594,0.071601,0.077671,0.092205,0.088385,0.066014,0.077771,0.16853],"unified_progress":[0.17442,0.06702,0.057569,0.059743,0.069071,0.072863,0.092149,0.086858,0.087289,0.075238,0.073473,0.084307]},{"section":15,"text":"It's a classic presentation for this condition.","dimension":3,"group":0,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.029034,0.044026,0.04966,0.054928,0.057872,0.061365,0.064156,0.064677,0.07103,0.086512,0.15819,0.25856],"unified_progress":[0.030057,0.048338,0.043601,0.062269,0.070349,0.073673,0.087469,0.084648,0.091076,0.10157,0.12566,0.18129]}],"qwq-